{"word":"G3560 - νουθετέω - nouthetéō - noo-thet-eh'-o - Admonish","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">νουθετέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">nouthetéō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">noo-thet-eh'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Admonish</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - புத்திசொல்"},{"paragraph":"to admonish, warn, exhort"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From the same as <a href=\"#/G3559 - νουθεσία - nouthesía - noo-thes-ee'-ah/3559\">G3559</a>; to <i>put in mind</i>, that is, (by implication) to <i>caution</i> or <i>reprove</i> gently: - admonish, warn.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}